talking about funny noises... I had a funny noise in the 65's engine, but 
only at a certain RPM ... like at 28mph in 3rd gear, not 27  or 29. It went away 
when I removed the fan belt... diagnosed as a fan rubbing... but only at a 
certain rpm... It was annoying, but knowing that it wasn't dangerous I didn't 
feel like fixing it right away. Eventually I put another shim in it, and the 
noise is gone.

Also... there was a friend who had a funny noise.. turned out there was some 
pin or something working it's way out of the case and being hit by the FW

good luck with the mystery, Inspector!

